  <preparation>Brown hamburger and onion together in skillet.  Remove from heat and mix in chili powder, tomato sauce, and corn.  Season with salt and pepper to taste.

Arrange a layer of tortillas on the bottom of casserole.  Put half of the sauce in a layer and top with chopped olives and grated cheese.  Repeat.

Bake at 325F for 30 minutes.</preparation>
